*.7z
# …but keep the slide skill's intentional archives (visual reference galleries).
# Icons used to live here as zips too, but were unpacked to assets/icons/ in
# 2026-04 — claude.ai's upload validator rejects nested zips. Scripts now
# resolve icons from assets/icons/<lib>/<name>.svg or the bundled essentials.
!.claude/skills/slide/references/jangpm-patterns.tar.gz
!.claude/skills/slide/templates/layouts/jangpm/assets/specimen/preview.tar.gz

